@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam roundCorner 15
skinparam ArrowColor #555555
[*] --> Rejected
Rejected --> Cancelled : process
Rejected : entry / log report
Cancelled --> Delivered : confirm
Delivered --> Shipped : update
Shipped --> Closed : approve
Shipped : entry / log report
Closed --> Processing : update
Closed : entry / log report
Processing --> [*]
@enduml